      "content": "okay i guess. i just hate the idea of going to the clinic and paying for an x-ray if i don't really have to. if i just follow the FIRE thing for like 3 or 4 days and it's still a bit sore but i can walk on it, i'm good to go right? like, i don't really need to get it checked out by a doctor if i can manage the pain and swelling myself?",
